1.1 Why another e-mail client?
==============================

Why does the world need another e-mail client?  Well, I'm not sure the
world _needs_ another one, but maybe _I_ do! I spend a _lot_ of time,
professionally and privately, dealing with e-mail and therefore, having
an efficient e-mail client is essential for me. Since none of the
existing ones worked the way I wanted, I created my own.

   Even while having been created for such selfish reasons, mu4e tries
hard to be as useful as possible for all its users - suggestions are
very welcome and are acted upon.


